BlobGraffiti is a game developed by Rahulky Studio. This app is provided as a free game and is intended for entertainment purposes only.

Information Collection and Use

BlobGraffiti does not collect or store any personally identifiable information.

The game may request access to certain device features for gameplay functionality:

Microphone: Used only to detect sound input (to pop blobs). Audio data is processed locally on the device and is never recorded, saved, or shared.

Camera (optional): If enabled, it is only used to display your real-world background during gameplay. No images or video are recorded, stored, or transmitted.

We do not collect, share, or sell any personal data.

Third-Party Services

BlobGraffiti may use third-party libraries or services provided by Google Play (for ads, achievements, or analytics). These services may collect certain data as described in their own privacy policies:

Google Play Services
AdMob

SECURITY
We Respect your privacy. Since we do not collect or transmit personal information, your data stays on your device. However, keep in mind that third-party services may have their own data-handling practices.

Children's Privacy
BlobGraffiti is suitable for general audiences but is not specifically targeted at children under 13. we do not knowingly collect data from children.

Changes To this privacy policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the app or on this page.

